</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Open the top cover. 
</p><note type="important" id="GUID-405B737B-0174-4E5B-8F9D-460B9EA7D70C" class="- topic/note "><p class="- topic/p ">Do not lean on the strip support. 
</p></note></li></ol></prereq><section id="GUID-E4895B67-7FC1-4974-A5C8-D34725505879" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title ">Required tools</title><ul id="UL_0492307DCD35442EAC71B8DA95C8A8E5" class="- topic/ul "><li id="LI_421ADE177A4748CB8EAE9311930065D8" class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Screwdriver Torx T20 
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Sheet of media
</p></li><li id="LI_929C0F12811B4096BB70DA320BD9C6C8" class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Protective gloves: 
<b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">Microflex</b> 93-260 gloves. 
</p></li></ul></section><section id="GUID-C02D66D1-E3CC-4BC2-95F8-775D93D93431" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title ">Warning / Caution</title><note type="caution" id="GUID-A97040BC-F110-4E4B-9CFF-E8082B9DA00E" class="- topic/note "><fig id="GUID-DB340B14-87E5-4FDB-8108-245D16C84FF1" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-FCF86E23-0DD4-40BC-ACDF-FF8ABA1E6502-low.png" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-FCF86E23-0DD4-40BC-ACDF-FF8ABA1E6502-low.png"/></fig><p class="- topic/p ">Avoid skin contact with ink: wear protective gloves. 
</p><fig id="GUID-7C716739-2AD7-42F8-8EF6-B28A8E7B1F76" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-D8099BBE-C3A2-4392-8B56-C532EDDD6073-low.png" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-D8099BBE-C3A2-4392-8B56-C532EDDD6073-low.png"/></fig><p class="- topic/p "> Protect your eyes from splashing ink: wear safety glasses. 
</p></note></section><section id="GUID-EC9C24D5-D455-4022-B616-D7FEF4DE0A1A" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title ">Illustration</title><fig id="GUID-E2FF997A-3D69-440D-8537-DC74947917A9" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-D59924AF-0085-44A2-8837-D3D98CBA2E2C-low.png" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-D59924AF-0085-44A2-8837-D3D98CBA2E2C-low.png"/></fig></section><section id="SECTION_427616E2BC854A41A6E33F1B8684D8A6" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title ">How to remove</title><table pgwide="1" id="TABLE_0BF2156EA25344A5ABD0556D855F2FC9" class="- topic/table "><tgroup align="left" outputclass="step" cols="3" class="- topic/tgroup "><colspec colname="col1" colnum="1" colwidth="10*" class="- topic/colspec "/><colspec colname="col2" colnum="2" colwidth="50*" class="- topic/colspec "/><colspec colname="col3" colnum="3" colwidth="40*" class="- topic/colspec "/><thead valign="top" class="- topic/thead "><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Step 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Action 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Remarks 
</p></entry></row></thead><tbody valign="top" class="- topic/tbody "><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">1 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Move the Printhead carriage to the left hand side.
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="GUID-EFF7AA67-52E2-4ED9-8BD3-AB79558E212A" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-0BA7038C-9FF2-4F26-A100-3092B69731A6-low.png" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-0BA7038C-9FF2-4F26-A100-3092B69731A6-low.png"/></fig></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">2 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Put a sheet on the platen and slide the curing carriage to the middle of the platen above the sheet. 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="GUID-7A988D65-1946-44CF-865F-5021890EA06E" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-6F5469AC-2256-41D6-854D-B2825411FFC4-low.png" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-6F5469AC-2256-41D6-854D-B2825411FFC4-low.png"/></fig></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">3 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><ol class="- topic/ol "><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Remove the cables from the 4 cable guides. 
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p "> Disconnect the connector of the sensor. 
</p></li></ol></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="GUID-F4452266-9AAF-432C-BCD2-3BE76332CB35" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-B0DA2529-3E22-4134-9803-A1038E93C185-low.png" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-B0DA2529-3E22-4134-9803-A1038E93C185-low.png"/></fig></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">4 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Remove 1 screw. 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="GUID-B1D705A6-02FC-49FD-9F94-196457F6C54D" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-E7EF2411-640E-4F1A-A2D7-97686CF44581-low.png" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-E7EF2411-640E-4F1A-A2D7-97686CF44581-low.png"/></fig></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">5 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p "> Remove the 4 screws. 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="GUID-25FB6FA6-77FF-468B-9D22-46A41B5D9B4E" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-5567A414-37FE-4DBE-8FB4-642C14953300-low.png" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-5567A414-37FE-4DBE-8FB4-642C14953300-low.png"/></fig></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">6 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Now the mirror assembly is loose from the curing carriage. 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="GUID-EC18E9E3-AEBF-4735-A0A9-06008A8B55EC" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-6E24305C-684B-4DBD-9D81-FD8CACF62E28-low.png" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-6E24305C-684B-4DBD-9D81-FD8CACF62E28-low.png"/></fig></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">7 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p "> Remove the 2 screws of the Post and Pin curing lamp. 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">The curing lamp is now free from the mirror. 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="GUID-0BEF0856-906F-4759-AA9C-FE0837639536" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-0ED797FD-CBB7-426A-B810-EA7CE51D8A2A-low.png" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-0ED797FD-CBB7-426A-B810-EA7CE51D8A2A-low.png"/></fig></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">8 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Remove the 2 screws of the crash sensor and the sensor bracket. 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="GUID-5B0985E9-6628-461D-BF1D-3F2331FF376C" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-25F1BCDF-D342-4850-A968-30389240690F-low.png" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-25F1BCDF-D342-4850-A968-30389240690F-low.png"/></fig><fig id="GUID-210AA0F6-B9F4-41B0-8761-8C3BFB747A1F" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-B1B927F0-8C0D-4888-B5FE-E74E2727F228-low.png" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-B1B927F0-8C0D-4888-B5FE-E74E2727F228-low.png"/></fig><fig id="GUID-AEF056AB-AE71-45CB-A800-D7337D466372" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-DCA1474E-C74F-43C6-B40E-647397866552-low.png" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-DCA1474E-C74F-43C6-B40E-647397866552-low.png"/></fig></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">9 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Remove top screw of the sensor bracket. 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="GUID-560D4156-0DB7-4112-880A-BDB059A63CCE" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-EC647B03-CE37-4C96-ABBB-B40A4A443440-low.png" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-EC647B03-CE37-4C96-ABBB-B40A4A443440-low.png"/></fig></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">10 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Remove lower 2 screws of the sensor bracket. 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="GUID-557129A0-5BFE-4BD6-863F-474EA2BF6B14" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-57A1BE6E-5C9F-4D9B-9C75-802D85969D04-low.png" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-57A1BE6E-5C9F-4D9B-9C75-802D85969D04-low.png"/></fig></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">11 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Remove the bracket form the mirror. 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="GUID-7BCE2818-042A-42BD-A705-8EABFF93E622" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-D41064D9-B6A3-4582-BC18-58FEB529BD1F-low.png" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-D41064D9-B6A3-4582-BC18-58FEB529BD1F-low.png"/></fig></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">12 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p "> Remove the mirror assembly. 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><fig id="GUID-B96EA771-CEB9-487A-BF96-75EFA1FA1597" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-0C1A7531-67A5-4BBE-A0CD-2D6331AEFD77-low.png" keyref="" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-0C1A7531-67A5-4BBE-A0CD-2D6331AEFD77-low.png"/></fig></entry></row></tbody></tgroup></table></section><section id="GUID-234D70A5-41EC-40E2-9E43-4217D346F540" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title ">How to install</title><table id="GUID-BDB87D50-9E70-4086-AC9E-FA7970C76B0D" pgwide="1" class="- topic/table "><tgroup align="left" outputclass="step" cols="3" class="- topic/tgroup "><colspec colname="col1" colnum="1" colwidth="10*" class="- topic/colspec "/><colspec colname="col2" colnum="2" colwidth="50*" class="- topic/colspec "/><colspec colname="col3" colnum="3" colwidth="40*" class="- topic/colspec "/><thead valign="top" class="- topic/thead "><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Step 
